Package: i3-gnome
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, desktop-file-utils, gnome-control-center, gnome-keyring, gnome-session
Description: i3-wm + GNOME Session infrastructure
 This package adds a new session type "i3 + GNOME" which allows
 you to start i3-wm and use the GNOME 3 Session infrastructure.
